The paper discusses the use of blockchain and DLTs to combat digital deception, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also mentions the potential economic and national security implications of digital deception, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of blockchain in storing and exchanging information, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
